<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idab1ed00a-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5" identifier="/us/usc/t10/s8333"><num value="8333">§ 8333.</num><heading> Computation of retired and retainer pay</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0" id="idab1ed00b-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5" identifier="/us/usc/t10/s8333/a"><num value="a">(a)</num><content> The monthly retired pay or retainer pay of a member entitled to such pay under this chapter or under section 8470 or 8372 of this title is computed in accordance with the following table.<html:table width="50%" style="border-collapse:collapse;  border-bottom:1px solid black; -uslm-lc: c4,L2,tp0,p6,6/7,xls30C,xls30C,r10,r10,tp0,p6,6/7,xls30C,xls30C,r10,r10; " id="idab1ed00c-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5">
<html:colgroup>
<html:col style="width:34pt ; max-width:34pt;" />
<html:col style="width:34pt ; max-width:34pt;" />
